item.title: Men's Green-Striped H'mong Brocade Outfit
item.description: The traditional attire of the H’mong people is very unique. In modern life, despite the influx of new, trendy fashion styles, H’mong ethnic outfits remain highly favored and sought after, especially for special events requiring ethnic elements or for artistic creation.
